title: Tokiko recounts her experience being detained as a Japanese American during WWII

media:group.media:title: Tokiko recounts her experience being detained as a Japanese American during WWII
media:group.media:description:
Tokiko, a “Being Asian in America” documentary participant, recounts her early memories of being detained with her family during WWII. 

This video is part of our “Being Asian in America” project. 
Watch the full documentary here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIIvqJDv6_4 
For more on the project, visit https://www.pewresearch.org/BeingAsianInAmerica
